title: Diomira
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Italian, Western, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has 6 to 8 veg items which are pastas and other vegetable dishes, plus a few veggie pizzas and salads. Nice, calm atmosphere, seems popular. Staff speaks English. Vegan items on menu are limited. Please let HappyCow know if veg-options are good enough to continue to list this business.
